		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The gimp provides this interface: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://docs.gimp.org/2.6/en/plug-in-colormap-remap.html">http://docs.gimp.org/2.6/en/plug-in-colormap-remap.html</a><!-- m -->

		

