	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Palette tools?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Or in GIMP: <ol style="list-style-type: decimal"><li>Create a new RGB image of the same size. </li><li>Fill it with the first color in the desired palette. </li><li>Image &gt; Mode &gt; Indexed and accept the defaults. </li><li>Open the colormap: Windows &gt; Dockable Dialogs &gt; Colormap. </li><li>For each color in order, choose the color in the color picker, then add it to the new image's colormap. </li><li>Paste something into this window. </li></ol>

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


